<span id="Description"></span>
==Beschreibung==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The '''Std Properties''' command displays the [[Property_editor|Property view panel]]. This panel is only available if the [[Preferences_Editor#General_2|Tree view and Property view mode]] preference is set to {{Value|Independent}}. If the preference is set to {{Value|Combined}}, or if the panel is already visible, this command has no effect.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Usage==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Select one or more objects.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Edit → [[Image:Std_Properties.svg|16px]] Properties}} option from the menu.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Std_Properties.svg|16px]] Properties}} option from the [[Tree_view|Tree view]] context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Alt}}+{{KEY|Enter}}.
# The Property view panel is displayed.
</div>


